  </div>
  <div class="case-grid" id="caseGrid"></div>

  <div class="section-head" style="margin-top:8px;">
    <div class="section-title"><span class="section-title-num">02</span>Anti-cases — what the architecture is <em style="font-style:italic;color:var(--accent);">not</em> for</div>
